UPDATE dbc_mailtemplate SET Subject_Lang_enGB='A New Year, A New Brew!', Body_Lang_enGB='Greetings $n!$b$b   We hope that the new year is treating you well.  If it isn''t, stop by our vendors to pick up the latest brew.  It is sure to bring out the animal in you.$b$b   Enjoy the samples and have a great new year!$b$b- Brew of the Month Club' WHERE ID=197;
UPDATE dbc_mailtemplate SET Subject_Lang_enGB='Can''t Keep A Good Brew Down.', Body_Lang_enGB='$n,$b$b   Sometimes you can''t keep a good brew down.  This new brew is good, but can you keep it down?$b$b   Remember, if you like these samples, you can get more from visiting our vendors.$b$bEnjoy!$b$b- Brew of the Month Club' WHERE ID=198;
UPDATE dbc_mailtemplate SET Subject_Lang_enGB='Some Buzz On The Latest Brew', Body_Lang_enGB='Hello $n,$b$b   Sometimes you want a fragrant brew, and what is a better aroma than honey?  Creatures great and small all love the sweet smell of honey.  Once you try this brew out, we think you''ll agree.$b$b   Remember, if you enjoyed these samples, you can purchase more from visiting our vendors.$b$bEnjoy!$b$b- Brew of the Month Club' WHERE ID=199;
UPDATE dbc_mailtemplate SET Subject_Lang_enGB='Because You Demanded It', Body_Lang_enGB='Greetings $n,$b$b   We''ve heard that some of our members wanted a brew that was a little more light and bubbly.  We''ve tried to tell them this isn''t the "Champagne of the Month Club."  Unfortunately, that didn''t stop the demand.  Hopefully this month''s brew will satisfy those that want a lighter and more bubbly brew.$b$b   Don''t forget, if you enjoyed this sample, it is available for purchase from our vendors.$b$bEnjoy!$b$b- Brew of the Month Club' WHERE ID=200;
UPDATE dbc_mailtemplate SET Subject_Lang_enGB='A Springtime Celebration!', Body_Lang_enGB='Hello $n,$b$b   Spring is definitely in the air, and this month you may find it underfoot!  Try out our new brew, Springtime Stout.  It''s a refreshing brew perfect for this time of year.$b$b  Enjoy the sample, and remember that you can visit our vendors to purchase more!$b$b- Brew of the Month Club' WHERE ID=201;
